										<content:encoded><![CDATA[<p><img decoding="async" class="alignnone size-full wp-image-209" src="https://itfeelsgoodtobelost.files.wordpress.com/2018/04/dsc03544.jpg" alt="DSC03544" width="4800" height="3200" /></p>
<p><img decoding="async" class="alignnone size-full wp-image-193" src="https://itfeelsgoodtobelost.files.wordpress.com/2018/04/london2.jpg" alt="london2" width="2592" height="1944" /></p>
<p style="text-align: center;">3, 2, 1&#8230; and go! We are leaving the place that was our home for the last 3,5 years. Crazy how much our lives have changed since we stepped our foot here for the first time&#8230;<br />
Now all our belongings fit into 2 backpacks and that&#8217;s what we call our new home <span class="_47e3 _5mfr" title="smile emoticon"><img decoding="async" class="img" role="presentation" src="https://static.xx.fbcdn.net/images/emoji.php/v9/feb/2/16/1f642.png" alt="" width="16" height="16" /> </span></p>
<p style="text-align: center;">Let the adventure begin!</p>
